aboutUs.title: vision
content: In a highly competitive and rapidly developing market relying on research and technology, our vision is to be the market leader in Egypt for our full range of products and to become a global player in the field of car refinishes paints.As KAPCI COATINGS guiding principles are; Integrity, sustainability, investing in people and environmentally friendly products. It is committed to enhancing its services and performance and leading the market in Africa and the Middle East by 2012.

aboutUs.title: Certifications 2
content: KAPCI COATINGS is certified for ISO 9001 – 2008 quality assurance system.
The company is granted the ISO 14001 – 2004 .
The company offering both certificates is the German company TUV.
KAPCI Laboratories is certified for ISO/IEC 17025 : 2017, in physical mechanical testing of paints and varnishes
Also KAPCI COATINGS has ISO 18001 for safety management.
